#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/qgis_gui.rst:50
msgid ""
"The Menu bar provides access to QGIS functions using standard hierarchical "
"menus. The Menus, their options, associated icons and keyboard shortcuts are"
" described below. The keyboard shortcuts can be reconfigured "
"(:menuselection:`Settings --> Keyboard Shortcuts`)."
